watchlist.Title: Poetic Justice
watchlist.Plot: In this movie, we see the world through the eyes of main character Justice (Janet Jackson), a young African-American poet. A mail carrier invites a few friends along for a long overnight delivery run.
watchlist.Awards: Nominated for 1 Oscar. Another 4 wins & 4 nominations.

watchlist.Title: Batman: Under the Red Hood
watchlist.Plot: There's a mystery afoot in Gotham City, and Batman must go toe-to-toe with a mysterious vigilante, who goes by the name of Red Hood. Subsequently, old wounds reopen and old, once buried memories come into the light.

watchlist.Title: To Sir, with Love
watchlist.Plot: Idealistic engineer-trainee and his experiences in teaching a group of rambunctious white high school students from the slums of London's East End.
